703685f-a.text:
Clinton Street, north from, but not including De Graw Street. This view shows Christ's Episcopal church on the left.

February 21, 1930.

P. L. Sperr.

241-253 Degraw Street, north side, from, but not including Clinton Street, to, but not including Tompkins Place. The view shows Trinity Evangelical Lutheran Church at No. 249.
February 21, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.

The same, from a different angle, showing only Nos. 249-253 Degraw
Street.
June 6, 1933.
